| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-3520 — Recovery Inhibition (blackbasta)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: f3b90130-e1dd-5f23-a027-8283c2e51c0a"
